snippet.title: Straight Outta Compton | "Yo Dre. I Got Somethin' to Say..."
snippet.description:
"Yo, Dre. I got somethin' to say." Watch N.W.A. face off against the Detroit police department after they perform "F*** Tha Police" in the 2015 biopic Straight Outta Compton!
#StraightOuttaCompton #NWA #IceCube

Buy/Rent Straight Outta Compton!
Amazon: https://www.amazon.com/dp/B013WF6OF4
iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/gb/movie/straight-outta-compton-2015/id1014666112
YouTube Movies: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jq1kJVE3Oaw
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/movies/details/Straight_Outta_Compton?id=jq1kJVE3Oaw&hl=en_US
Fandango Now: https://www.fandangonow.com/details/movie/straight-outta-compton-2015/MMV97873BEEB1DC6EA1FDFAD0CEBCB51E97F
VUDU: https://www.vudu.com/content/movies/details/Straight-Outta-Compton/682874
Universal Pictures Home Entertainment: https://www.uphe.com/movies/straight-outta-compton

Straight Outta Compton tells the true story of how five young cultural rebels - armed only with their lyrics, swagger, bravado and raw talent - stood up to the authorities that meant to keep them down and formed the world's most dangerous group, N.W.A. And as they spoke the truth that no one had before and exposed life in the hood, their voice ignited a social revolution that is still reverberating today.

© 2015 Universal Studios. All Rights Reserved.
Cast: O'Shea Jackson Jr., Corey Hawkins, Jason Mitchell, Neil Brown Jr., Aldis Hodge, Paul Giamatti
Produced By: Ice Cube, Tomica Woods-Wright, Matt Alvarez, F. Gary Gray, Scott Bernstein, Dr. Dre
Directed By: F. Gary Gray
